msgid "index"
msgstr ""
"<h1>Application for reading ebooks – FBReader</h1>\n"
"\n"
"<br>\n"
"1) Reading ebooks\n"
"<br>\n"
"2) Settings\n"
"<br>\n"
"3) Book menu\n"
"<br>\n"
"4) About\n"

msgid "fbreader1"
msgstr ""
"<h2>Reading ebooks:</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>To navigate between pages of the text use joystick buttons left/right,"
" as well as “5”/”6” number buttons. Functions of the programmable buttons"
" can be changed by selecting “Keys” in “ Settings” menu.</p> \n"
"<p>To change orientation of the page (portrait/landscape), press “Rotate”"
" button. Functions of joystick buttons changes to fit the new "
"orientation. </p> \n"
"<p>To search in the text, press “Search/Zoom” button. Virtual keyboard "
"appears. Press programmable button according to the number of the row and"
" then according to the number of the column to enter the phrase to "
"search. To search next or previous press joystick buttons right/left. To "
"exit from the search mode, press “OK” button.</p>\n"
"<p>To view and change settings of the FBReader, press “ОК” to proceed to "
"the “Settings” menu.</p>\n"
"<p>To view and change settings of the text file, press “M” button to "
"proceed to the “Book menu”.</p>\n"
"<p>The Help can be opened by pressing “0” button.</p> \n"
"<p>To control playing of the audio file while you are reading ebooks, use"
" “Play/Stop” button, located in lower right side of the device.</p>\n"

msgid "fbreader4"
msgstr ""
"<h2>About:</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>FBReader – application for reading ebooks. Supports formats: fb2, "
"html, xhtml, docbook.</p>\n"

msgid "fbreader3"
msgstr ""
"<h2>Book menu:</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>You can display the book information, jump to a page, display table of"
" contents, search words in the text, and put bookmarks in the book.</p>\n"

msgid "fbreader2"
msgstr ""
"<h2>Settings:</h2>\n"
"\n"
"<p>In this menu you can view and change:</p>\n"
"<p>Format – settings of the style of the text of ebook;</p>\n"
"<p>Indicator – settings of the indicator;</p>\n"
"<p>Language – settings of the language and encoding of the text as "
"defaults;</p>\n"
"<p>Book settings – settings of the language and encoding of the text of "
"the current ebook;</p>\n"
"<p>Keys – settings of the functions of “1-9” programmable keys.</p>\n"

